      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it doesn't feel like a victory. it just feels like being trapped. like i'm just stuck in this body that's constantly screaming at me and there's no way to make it stop. sometimes i look at it and i just think... wouldn't it be such a mercy if everything just went quiet? if i didn't have to wake up to this every single day?",
